# Custom Kernel Configurations
#
# This directory is for your custom kernel configuration files.
# They work the same as official configs in ../. but are gitignored.
#
# Example:
#   cp ../harper_deb13_tune.config ./my_custom_tune.config
#   # Edit my_custom_tune.config as needed
#   # Then reference it in your params file:
#   TUNING_CONFIG="configs.d/my_custom_tune.config"
#
# The system automatically checks configs.d/ first, then falls back to configs/.
